# Studio design system feature flag.
#
# Default (unset): the new Studio app shell is ON — quiet rail + 40px topbar
# + Cmd-K palette + bg-paper canvas. Backend, integrations, slices, and
# existing routes are unaffected.
#
# To temporarily fall back to the legacy 240px dark sidebar Layout:
#   VITE_NEW_SHELL=0
#
# (The legacy Layout file remains in the codebase as a one-flag fallback.)

# The /pipeline route is additive — registered regardless of the flag.
# Visit /org/:slug/pipeline for the new home, or /org/:slug/internal/uikit
# for the design-system reference page.
